CLASS-->
	The "class" is used to unify all the attributes in css style sheets linked from the respective htmlpage using the proper synatx.
	_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
	for example(code in html & css)-->
		<p class="textmod">Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quibusdam, dolore illo veritatis dicta, obcaecati nostrum quis nesciunt eius velit asperiores quae voluptas impedit pariatur vero recusandae repellat reprehenderit corporis in.</p>
